slike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:37:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8f7933a097cbb6f3d9eef349ce6d918e08b71ee","tid":1595452,"uid":221192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:46:40.000Z","msg":"其實就咁唔理佢個對話可能真係會出事 <br />\n<br />\n今朝睇now新聞訪問左個被抽中既人，講廣東話但聽得出有少少口音，內容大致就係話好同意抗爭呀，但再咁落去都唔係辦法，所以無論對話定示威都一齊做呀，又話政府咁樣做係個好開始乜乜乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71bd0f7cc1f17f7052e91caf6581333ccb01cfc","tid":1595452,"uid":99172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"你個標題太差 重開啦<br />\n認同終極和理非<br />\n好似星期五晚遮打啲集會咁<br />\n坐喺地叫口號舉牌<br />\n但唔好叫仇警口號 還眼嗰啲 <br />\n冇意義得自high  仲會provoke班癲狗"},{"pid":"bbbb0f9fd9b7091d9dfea7a755a5266bc59e4b03","tid":1595452,"uid":263038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:49:47.000Z","msg":"推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e874f67caf62098f1e980e4eb0feca5574a32b","tid":1595452,"uid":115987,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:50:07.000Z","msg":"On9 去乜撚"},{"pid":"2ea721ed2706efc99efc660b385572bc9141d1a6","tid":1595452,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:51:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">盡block 標題黨</span>"},{"pid":"29667b42fde8b4b103b1c34077dc5cec6a0c6cc6","tid":1595452,"uid":172137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:53:18.000Z","msg":"推 支持<br />\n今晚伊館要人<br />\n圍撚林鄭臭閪"},{"pid":"0da6e111e8474552f696afec07483c1b44c28983","tid":1595452,"uid":280752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"叫口號屌鳩淋病"}]}